dia-scholarship\/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tMEDIA\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/sorayah.-Public-Policy-1-e1618854726569.jpg\" alt=\"sorayah. Public Policy (1)\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"768\" width=\"960\" title=\"sorayah. Public Policy (1)\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/internship\/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPOLICY\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t<h2><strong>Stay updated on what&#8217;s happening at ISF!<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Support a New Chapter of Muslim Progress Your Support Elevates American Muslim Voices &#8211; Donate Before the Year Ends Donate Now 2022 Annual Report See ISF alums&#8217; amazing work and the access we provide through your support. Read ISF&#8217;s Annual Report Representation in Positions that Matter ISF increases American Muslim representation in media, film, government,&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":28518,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v21.7 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Home - Islamic Scholarship Fund<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"The Islamic Scholarship Fund empowers American Muslim leaders in policy, law, media, and film to create a world where race, religion, gender, and socioeconomic status are no longer barriers to equity and equality. ISF scholars are agents of change at the epicenters of institutions that impact public opinion and policy.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:loc